<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="utf-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>Welcome to UniTrack - {{teacherName}}</title>
  <style>
    body {
      font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, "Segoe UI", Roboto, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;
      background: #f9f9f9;
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
      color: #1d1d1f;
    }
    .email-wrapper {
      max-width: 600px;
      margin: 40px auto;
      background: #fff;
      border-radius: 12px;
      overflow: hidden;
      box-shadow: 0 4px 20px rgba(0,0,0,0.08);
    }
    .header {
      text-align: center;
      padding: 32px 20px 20px;
    }
    .header h1 {
      font-size: 24px;
      font-weight: 600;
      margin: 10px 0;
      color: #000;
    }
    .subtitle {
      font-size: 15px;
      color: #6e6e73;
    }
    .content {
      padding: 28px 24px;
      font-size: 15px;
      line-height: 1.6;
    }
    .greeting {
      font-size: 17px;
      font-weight: 600;
      margin-bottom: 14px;
    }
    .credentials-container {
      background: #f5f5f7;
      border-radius: 10px;
      padding: 16px;
      margin: 24px 0;
    }
    .credentials-title {
      font-size: 15px;
      font-weight: 600;
      margin-bottom: 10px;
    }
    .credential-item {
      margin: 6px 0;
      font-size: 14px;
    }
    .credential-label {
      font-weight: 500;
      margin-right: 6px;
    }
    .credential-value {
      font-family: SFMono-Regular, Consolas, monospace;
      background: #e5e5ea;
      padding: 2px 6px;
      border-radius: 6px;
    }
    .steps {
      margin: 24px 0;
    }
    .steps-title {
      font-size: 15px;
      font-weight: 600;
      margin-bottom: 10px;
    }
    .step {
      margin: 8px 0;
      font-size: 14px;
    }
    .cta {
      text-align: center;
      padding: 28px;
      background: #f9f9f9;
    }
    .cta-button {
      background: #000;
      color: #fff;
      padding: 12px 28px;
      text-decoration: none;
      font-weight: 600;
      font-size: 15px;
      border-radius: 8px;
      display: inline-block;
      margin-top: 10px;
    }
    .footer {
      text-align: center;
      padding: 18px;
      font-size: 12px;
      color: #6e6e73;
      border-top: 1px solid #e5e5ea;
      background: #fafafa;
    }

    /* Dark mode */
    @media (prefers-color-scheme: dark) {
      body { background: #000; color: #f5f5f7; }
      .email-wrapper { background: #1c1c1e; box-shadow: none; }
      .header h1 { color: #fff; }
      .subtitle { color: #a1a1a6; }
      .content { color: #f5f5f7; }
      .credentials-container { background: #2c2c2e; }
      .credential-value { background: #3a3a3c; color: #f5f5f7; }
      .steps-title { color: #fff; }
      .step { color: #f5f5f7; }
      .cta { background: #1c1c1e; }
      .cta-button { background: #fff; color: #000; }
      .footer { background: #1c1c1e; color: #a1a1a6; border-top: 1px solid #2c2c2e; }
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="email-wrapper">
    <div class="header">
      <div style="font-size:40px;">ðŸŽ“</div>
      <h1>UniTrack</h1>
      <div class="subtitle">Attendance. Simplified.</div>
    </div>
    <div class="content">
      <div class="greeting">Hello {{teacherName}}, ðŸ‘‹</div>
      <p>Welcome to UniTrack. Your account is ready.</p>
      <div class="credentials-container">
        <div class="credentials-title">Your Credentials</div>
        <div class="credential-item"><span class="credential-label">Email:</span><span class="credential-value">{{teacherEmail}}</span></div>
        <div class="credential-item"><span class="credential-label">Password:</span><span class="credential-value">{{temporaryPassword}}</span></div>
      </div>
      <div class="steps">
        <div class="steps-title">Getting Started</div>
        <div class="step">1. Log in with your credentials</div>
        <div class="step">2. Create your courses</div>
        <div class="step">3. Start attendance sessions</div>
        <div class="step">4. View and export reports</div>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="cta">
      <a href="{{loginUrl}}" class="cta-button">Access Dashboard</a>
    </div>
    <div class="footer">
      UniTrack Support Team â€¢ Contact us anytime
    </div>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
